ConfigurationOptions.Summary: Designed to give you bare-bones monitoring for your environment. Attempts to reduce alerts to actionable items at a risk of missing some proactive notifications.
Designed to provide additional monitoring and performance collection over essentials, while still reducing unnecessary noise from the default and full tuning options
Includes alerts for more unique and specific conditions as well as some increased monitoring and performance collection intervals

Description: Internet Information Services (IIS) 10. Shipped with Server 2016. Captured using V10.1.0.0 of the MP.
